window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Returning to the town of my childhood abduction to settle my late father's estate proves more challenging than expected.</b><br> <br> On my first day, a chilling note labeled \"Little Moth\" sparks unsettling events. The notes soon lead to ominous phone calls and a lurking presence outside my windows. I suspect the stalker could be Sheriff Banner, tangled in my father's past, fire chief Dale Watchman, or even the firefighter who saved me years ago. Someone watches me sleep, lurks outside my darkened windows, yet vanishes without a trace when confronted. Despite warnings to leave, I, Vanessa Elizabeth Harper, am determined to confront my fears.<br> <br> In a town where shadows hold secrets, my past threatens to become my future.</p>"; 
